quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  20,91,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A ò níí yé dúró sọ́dọ̀ rẹ̀ tí a óò máa jọ́sìn fún un títí (Ànábì) Mūsā yóò fi padà sọ́dọ̀ wa.”"
  20,92,"(Ànábì) Mūsā sọ pé: “Hārūn, kí ni ó kọ̀ fún ọ nígbà tí o rí wọn tí wọ́n ṣìnà"
  20,93,"láti tọ̀ mí wá? Ṣé o yapa àṣẹ mi ni?”"
  21,67,"Ṣíọ̀ ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún lẹ́yìn Allāhu, ṣé ẹ̀yin kò níí ṣe làákàyè ni?"
  21,68,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ẹ dáná sun ún; kí ẹ sì ran àwọn ọlọ́hun yín lọ́wọ́, tí ẹ̀yin bá níkan-án ṣe.”"
  21,69,"A sọ pé: “Iná, di tútù àti àlàáfíà lára ’Ibrọ̄hīm.”"
  22,43,"Àti pé ìjọ ’Ibrọhīm àti ìjọ (Ànábì) Lūt,"
  22,44,"àti àwọn ará ìlú Mọdyan (àwọn náà ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Wọ́n tún pe (Ànábì) Mūsā ní òpùrọ́. Mo sì lọ́ àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ lára. Lẹ́yìn náà, Mo gbá wọn mú. Báwo sì ni bí Mo ṣe (fi ìyà) kọ (aburú fún wọn) ti rí!"
  22,45,"Nítorí náà, mélòó mélòó nínú ìlú tí A ti parẹ́ nígbà tí wọ́n jẹ́ alábòsí; àwọn ilé wọn dàwó lulẹ̀ pẹ̀lú òrùlé rẹ̀. (Mélòó mélòó nínú) kànǹga tí wọ́n ti patì (nípasẹ̀ ìparun) àti ilé pẹ̀tẹ́ẹ̀sì oníbíríkì (tó ti dahoro)!"
  23,19,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A fi dá àwọn ọgbà oko dàbínù àti àjàrà fún yín; ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ èso wà nínú rẹ̀ fún yín, ẹ sì ń jẹ nínú rẹ̀."
  23,20,"Àti igi kan tó ń hù jáde níbi àpáta Sīnā’; ó ń mú epo àti n̄ǹkan ìṣebẹ̀ jáde fún àwọn tó ń jẹ ẹ́."
  23,21,"Àti pé dájúdájú àríwòye wà fún yín lára àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn; À ń fún yín mu nínú ohun tí ó wà nínú ikùn wọn. Àwọn àǹfààní ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ (mìíràn) tún wà fún yín lára wọn, ẹ sì ń jẹ nínú rẹ̀."
  24,1,"(Èyí ni) Sūrah kan tí A sọ̀kalẹ̀. A ṣe ìdájọ́ inú rẹ̀ ní òfin (dandan). A sì sọ àwọn āyah tó yanjú kalẹ̀ sínú rẹ̀ nítorí kí ẹ lè lo ìrántí."
  24,2,"Onísìná lóbìnrin àti onísìná lọ́kùnrin, ẹ na ẹnì kọ̀ọ̀kan nínú àwọn méjèèjì ní ọgọ́rùn-ún kòbókò. Ẹ má ṣe jẹ́ kí àánú wọn ṣe yín nípa ìdájọ́ Allāhu tí ẹ bá ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú Allāhu àti Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn. Kí igun kan nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo sì jẹ́rìí sí ìyà àwọn méjèèjì.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ọgọ́rùn-ún kòbókò àti ẹ̀wọ̀n ọdún kan tàbí ọgọ́rùn-ún kòbókò àti lílé kúrò nínú ìlú fún ọdún kan ni ìjìyà fún onísìná tí kò ì ṣe ‘akdu-nnikāh pẹ̀lú ẹnikẹ́ni rí. Àmọ́ lílẹ̀ lókòpa ni ìjìyà fún onísìná tí ó ti ṣe ‘akdu-nnikāh rí. Ẹ̀dá ìbá mọ ìjìyà wọ̀nyí lọ́ràn, ìbá jìnnà sí àgbèrè ṣíṣe. Ìwọ arákùnrin àti arábìnrin mi, bí ọ̀ràn sìná bá fúyẹ́ ni, ìbá tí la ìjìyà lọ bí kò ṣe títọrọ àforíjìn lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ -.]
  24,3,"Onísìná lọ́kùnrin kò níí ṣe sìná pẹ̀lú ẹnì kan bí kò ṣe onísìná lóbìnrin (ẹgbẹ́ rẹ̀) tàbí ọ̀ṣẹbọ lóbìnrin. Onísìná lóbìnrin, ẹnì kan kò níí bá a ṣe sìná bí kò ṣe onísìná lọ́kùnrin (ẹgbẹ́ rẹ̀) tàbí ọ̀ṣẹbọ lọ́kùnrin.A sì ṣe ìyẹn (sìná ṣíṣe) ní èèwọ̀ fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.2 {1}",footnotes:1:[N̄ǹkan mẹ́ta ni kalmọh “nikāh” dúró fún. Ìkíní, “ ‘aƙdu-nnikāh”; ìtúmọ̀ rẹ̀ ni “ìtakókó yìgì, síso yìgì tàbí ìgbéyàwó”. Èyí ni kí waliyyu (aláṣẹ) obìnrin sọ fún ọkùnrin kan pé, “Mo fi ọmọbìnrin tí orúkọ rẹ̀ ń jẹ́ lágbájá fún ọ, kí o fi ṣe ìyàwó.” Gbólóhùn yìí lè wáyé yálà nípasẹ̀ kí ọkùnrin náà bèèrè fún un pé, “Ẹ fún mi ní ọmọbìnrin tí orúkọ rẹ̀ ń jẹ́ lágbájá kí n̄g fi ṣe ìyàwó.” (ìyẹn síwájú gbólóhùn waliyyu obìnrin náà) tàbí kí ọkùnrin náà sọ pé, “Mo tẹ́wọ́ gbà á láti fi ṣe ìyàwó” (ìyẹn lẹ́yìn gbólóhùn waliyyu). Gbólóhùn ti waliyyu àti gbólóhùn ti ọkùnrin náà ni a mọ̀ sí “gbólóhùn ìtakókó yìgì.]
